English: This field of research allows a nation to develop weapons and materials for its infantry personnel. It includes hand-held weapons and special equipment allowing the construction of Marines and Paratroops. But perhaps most importantly, this field of research will allow the development of proper field engineering equipment and improved logistics and command systems. This field is vital  if you want good infantry, paras and marines.

Il s'agit notamment d'armes de poing et d'йquipements spйciaux qui permettent d'entraоner des unitйs d'assaut amphibie et des parachutistes. Plus important encore, ce domaine de recherche mиne а la mise au point de nouvelles techniques pour le gйnie, la logistique et les systиmes de commandement. Les recherches sur l'infanterie sont cruciales pour toutes les nations engagйes dans la guerre.

Sono incluse armi a mano ed equipaggiamenti speciali, che consentono la produzione di marine e paracadutisti. Forse perт la cosa piщ importante и che questo campo di ricerca permette lo sviluppo di un equipaggiamento di ingegneria da campo adeguato e sistemi logistici e di comando migliorati. Questo settore risulta fondamentale per disporre di una buona fanteria, oltre che di paracadutisti e marine esperti.

English: This field of research allows a nation to develop heavy weapons and materials for its units. It includes cannon and special vehicles allowing the construction of Artillery and Rocket Artillery units. But perhaps most importantly, this field of research will allow the development of tanks and early armored personnel carriers with the speed, protection and firepower to break through enemy lines. This is field is vital if you want good tank divisions and artillery brigades.
French: Ce domaine de recherche permet а une nation de mettre au point des armes et des йquipements lourds destinйs а ses unitйs. Il s’agit notamment de cannons et de vйhicules spйciaux qui permettent de mettre au point de l’artillerie et des unitйs de lance-roquettes. Plus important encore, ce domaine de recherche mиne а la mise au point de chars et de premiers vйhicules blindйs de transport du personnel avec la rapiditй, la protection et la puissance de feu nйcessaire pour briser les lignes ennemies. Ces recherches sont cruciales si vous voulez de bonnes divisions de chars et de bonnes brigades d’artillerie.

Comprende cannoni e veicoli speciali e consente di realizzare unitа di artiglieria e lanciamissili. La cosa piщ importante и che queste ricerche servono anche per l'ideazione dei primi carri e dei trasporti truppe corazzati, dotati di protezione, velocitа e potenza di fuoco per sfondare le linee nemiche. Si tratta di un campo di ricerche vitale, se vuoi avere divisioni corazzate e brigate di artiglieria efficaci.

Incluye caсones y vehнculos especiales y posibilita la construcciуn de unidades de artillerнa y de artillerнa lanzacohetes. Pero quizб mбs importante sea que este campo de investigaciуn permitirб el desarrollo de carros de combate (tanques) y de los primeros transportes blindados de personal, con la velocidad, la protecciуn y la potencia de fuego necesarias para atravesar las lнneas enemigas. Este campo es vital si quieres buenas divisiones de tanques y brigadas de artillerнa.
German: Dieses Forschungsfeld ermцglicht es einer Nation schwere Waffen und Materialen fьr ihre Einheiten zu entwickeln. Es schlieЯt gepanzerte und Spezialfahrzeuge ein, die die Herstellung von Artillerie- und Raketenartillerie-Einheiten erlaubt. Doch vielleicht das Wichtigste in diesem Forschungsfeld ist die Entwicklung von Panzern und frьhen gepanzerten Mannschaftswagen mit der Geschwindigkeit, dem Schutz und der Feuerkraft, um feindliche Linien zu durchbrechen. Dieses Feld ist fьr die Herstellung guter Panzerdivisionen und Artilleriebrigaden дuЯerst wichtig.

This field is vital if you want good aircraft and air superiority is important if you are to win the war.

English: This field of research allows a nation to develop a naval power projection capability. If your war effort relies either upon defeating the enemy by projecting your own power over the sea, or by denying the enemy the ability to project his own power, this field is vital. Research will allow a nation to build large capital ships, such as Battleships and Aircraft Carriers, and smaller warships, like Destroyers and Submarines.

English: These land doctrines were introduced sometimes by directives based on theoretical knowledge and sometimes by a trial and error process. They cover the tactical, organizational and strategic aspects of land combat. There are alternatives  representing different cultural outlooks but also need. A focus on Mobility allows a choice between the blitzkrieg used by the German Wehrmacht and the mass-combat assaults used by the Red Army. A focus on Firepower allows a choice between the offensive fire and movement favoured by the US Army and a more defensive doctrine based upon WWI fighting. The latter provides three different versions of firepower doctrine used by the British, the French and the Japanese.
French: Ces doctrines terrestres йtaient parfois introduites par des directives qui s’appuyaient sur des connaissances thйoriques, voire par des essais empiriques et des processus de recherches et d’erreurs. Elles englobent toutes les aspects tactiques, organisationnels et stratйgique du combat terrestre. Cette arborescence dispose de branches exclusives et sйparйes, qui reprйsentent les diffйrences des perspectives contextuelles et culturelles, mais aussi les besoins. English: These naval doctrines were introduced sometimes by directives based on theoretical knowledge and sometimes by a trial and error process. They cover the tactical, organizational and strategic aspects of naval combat. There are three main choices of doctrine.  Base Strike doctrine results in an offensive navy with excellent carrier capability. Fleet-in-Being doctrine gives the ability to protect and defend sealanes, and results in a strong surface-combat navy. Sealane Interdiction doctrine gives an excellent ability to destroy enemy convoys using submarines and surface-combat commerce raiders.
French: Ces doctrines navales avaient parfois introduites par des directives qui s’appuyaient sur des connaissances thйoriques, voire par des essais empiriques et des processus de recherches et d’erreurs. Elles englobent toutes les aspects tactiques, organisationnels et stratйgique du combat naval. Cette arborescence dispose de branches exclusives et sйparйes, qui reprйsentent les diffйrences, non seulement des perspectives contextuelles et culturelles, mais aussi les besoins. Les rйsultats de la Frappe de base donnent une marine offensive avec d’excellentes capacitйs porte-avions. L’itinйraire du parc naval vous donne la possibilitй de protйger et de dйfendre les voies maritimes, et donne donc une marine de surface forte et orientйe offensives.
